3755, "(fr)Good work Erikson. Ross, that's your target. Assault the Vehemence and try to disrupt that gravity generator."

3756, "(fr)Captain Lau, this is Lightowler. My crew are in the auxiliary transports. We're commencing detachment from the Pillar."

3757, "(fr)Reactor down! Did that work Lau?"

3758, "(fr)Good work Ross. That seems to have done the trick. Plotting course out of the Veil."

3759, "(fr)Bring yourself to dock. We'll jump as soon as you're secure."

3760, "(fr)<intercepted> Biranos. There's the mercenary whore, as well as her Renewal friends."

