3762, "(fr)Not every one of these pioneers made it back, but a few told stories of this Gaia in the Veil. Eventually it was dismissed as a mirage or fabrication, but the Children still believed."

3763, "(fr)We've got too many Malikan guns on us! Meiks, Ross, can you see if you can redirect some of that fire?"

