4565, "(fr)To the officers and crews of the FNS Colossus and FNS Artémis, this is Rear Admiral Akrami.

The Sinarus Combine have suffered a comprehensive defeat. Task Force 55 has repelled the Excelsior battlegroup from Élam space and the capital system of Akkad remains secure. Our tactical and strategic superiority over our old rivals remains indisputable.

