5009, "(fr)Stuart lad. A swear if ye're still at Akrotiri drinkin yourself tae an early grave A'm gaunae personally come oer thare an drive a boot up yer arse."

5010, "(fr)Where the hell have ye been? A've heard nothing from ye."

