5014, "(fr)It's out in Sulsia. A know it's a shithole in the middle of nowhere but it's a fresh start."

5015, "(fr)Get yer arse out of Akrotiri and come take this job wae me. Ye've got the skills for it and a could use someone familiar tae watch ma back. It'll also give ye a chance tae make a difference again."

