5049, "(fr)Kaur"

5050, "(fr)Hello Ross. Derek Kaur, ship's engineer. I helped Lau outfit the Hoshikuzu with the new reactor."

5051, "(fr)As a reward Lau now has me running double duty on reactor and gunship maintenance. I'm in charge of keeping your craft maintained and repaired."

5052, "(fr)I don't know if Lau told you. I used to serve in the Sinarus Combine navy. I was a flight deck engineer on an aviation frigate during the Great War."

5053, "(fr)I also know relations between our nations are strained. It's no matter. Sinarus, Alban, on this ship all are brothers. Leave the politics to the politicians."

5054, "(fr)Your gunships are interesting machines. I've modified their weapon mounts to accept most weapon systems out there. That should increase their potential firepower."

5055, "(fr)Right now we are limited to basic equipment. I expect things will change when we get access to more advanced weapons."

