5061, "(fr)No details on what to expect, but the Hoshikuzu and your gunships should have more than enough firepower to deal with any raiders we're likely to encounter. Your gunships are fully stocked with kinetic rounds and missiles."

5062, "(fr)Our mission is to safeguard the Compass Rose and her cargo while rendering assistance to her crew."

5063, "(fr)This is going to be your first outing with us, so I'll go through the game plan once more before we head out."

5064, "(fr)Your gunships are too small to have their own hyperspace impeller, so you two will ride docked on the Hoshikuzu's fighter rails when we enter hyperspace."

5065, "(fr)Once we enter the area, undock your gunships from the Hoshikuzu to initiate flight operations."

5066, "(fr)You'll be weapons free after that. Watch your fire though, the Hoshikuzu may be armoured but I don't want her to take any more damage than she needs to."

5067, "(fr)That's all for now. If there's no questions, get to your gunships. We jump when you're confirmed secure."

