5222, "(fr)Lieutenant Ross. I hear your group was responsible for getting us out of Sulsia alive. Thank you. The Crown is grateful for your efforts."

5223, "(fr)The loss of the Elgin was tragic but our embassy in Sulsia managed to evacuate with minimal casualties."

5224, "(fr)This attack on Commonwealth citizens wasn't a random Malikan raid. I'm afraid I must take partial responsibility."

5225, "(fr)Well-armed and well-resourced groups are after me, and unfortunately Commonwealth citizens were caught in the crossfire. When one can't find one's target, carpet bomb the ground around them and to hell with collateral damage."

5226, "(fr)I've come into information that certain powerful high-ups don't want released. Something to do with the Malikans' newfound capacity for war. As bad as the Sulsians are at keeping their own territory secure, they're not entirely to blame."

5227, "(fr)I was sent to find out who was supplying Andri Gadaria with weapons. The Malikans are a pawn in a greater game. We're now starting to find out who the players are."

5228, "(fr)The Crown may have need of your services soon. You can play at being mercenaries for a little while longer but don't drag your feet when Fleet calls. You still have your oath."

5229, "(fr)One more thing. The next time you two want to announce your Commonwealth credentials in public why don't you tight beam Admiral Romanowska into the conversation. Just for completion."

5230, "(fr)Welcome everyone."

5231, "(fr)Repair drones from Hopewell have attended to the Renewal convoy. We are now on final approach to Covenant."

5232, "(fr)For those who have never been to Covenant, you're in for a sight."

5233, "(fr)Covenant isn't a system or a planet. It's a hyperspace capable habitat that's a hub for transports, freighters and refinery ships all in service with the Children of Renewal."

5234, "(fr)I've been there before. The Children of Renewal are good people. The refugees will be well looked after."

5235, "(fr)Our job will be done once we arrive in Covenant. Once our payment comes through, I plan to find a Commonwealth port to drop off Kendra."

5236, "(fr)The Nassau, Hopewell and Pollux Arrow are free to pick up extra contracts at Covenant to pay for running costs."

5237, "(fr)Thanks Lau. We should be fine for a while. The bonus pay promised by Reverend Lightowler is substantial. Almost unexpectedly so."

5238, "(fr)Interesting. I get the feeling Lightowler's free with his credits because he doesn't see a need for them anymore."

5239, "(fr)The Children of Renewal must be planning something big."

5240, "(fr)Good luck to them. In the meantime, we've decided Ross, Meiks and Lau will run escort during the final approach. Our fighters got shot up pretty bad during the escape from Vicare and several of our pilots are recuperating."

5241, "(fr)Ambassador Hayburn assures me he will negotiate transport for the Alban citizens and Lightowler will represent the rest of the Sulsian refugees."

5242, "(fr)All we have to do is provide security for the approach and subsequent personnel transfer."

